'''EVS-469''' was an [[EVS Construction Droid]] which was hijacked by members of [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]] under [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]] as part of the Rogues' efforts to bring down the [[Planetary shield/Legends|planetary shields]] surrounding [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] in order to make way for the impending [[Liberation of Coruscant (Galactic Civil War)|invasion]] of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] capital world in [[7 ABY/Legends|7 ABY]]. The droid was used to transport the Rebels to one of the planet's subsidiary computer centers where they took control of one of Corusacnt's [[Orbital Solar Energy Transfer Satellite|orbital mirror]] stations. This was the key first step in the Rogues' plan to take down the shields, an attempt which proved to be a success.

